    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L V8 engine, known for its 8,400 RPM redline and individual throttle bodies. This unit utilizes the M Double-Clutch Transmission (M-DCT) with Drivelogic, providing lightning-fast gear changes and seamless power delivery to the M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), offering three stages of damping to manage the MacPherson strut front and five-link rear suspension geometry. While the exterior shows minor road-derived character consistent with its mileage, the powertrain remains robust, delivering linear torque and an exceptional power-to-weight ratio for the purist driver.",
