      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a reliable ride that's been well-loved? This beauty is ready for a new home! It runs like a dream and still looks fantastic\u2014just a few minor signs of being enjoyed over the years, but it\u2019s got so much life left in it. I\u2019ve taken really good care of it, and I\u2019m sure you\u2019ll love it as much as I have. It's perfect for those weekend road trips or just zipping around town. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
